OL,5, The Blue singer Lee Ryan has been      
OL,6, convicted of the racially aggravated   
OL,7, assault of a flight cabin crew member. 
OL,9,FRyan, 39, had drunk a bottle of port   
OL,10,Fbefore boarding a flight to London City
OL,11,FAirport on 31 July, Ealing Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt heard.                           
OL,14,FThe pop star had been eating cheese and
OL,15,Fdrinking alcohol in an airport lounge  
OL,16,Fbefore boarding the plane, the court   
OL,17,Fwas told.                              
OL,19,FRyan, who denied the charge, said his  
OL,20,Fbehaviour on the plane was "playful".  
